Output demo/demo.gif
Set Shell bash
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 900
Set Height 500
Set Padding 20
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"

Hide
Type "PS1='$ '"
Enter
Type "alias rtfm=~/.rtfm/demo/mock-rtfm.sh"
Enter
Type "clear"
Enter
Sleep 500ms
Show

Type@75ms 'rtfm "SDL3 create window"'
Sleep 500ms
Enter

Sleep 8s
